text: Musa Bihi Abdi (born 1948) is a Somaliland politician and former military officer. He has been President of Somaliland since December 2017. On 21 November 2017, Muse Bihi was announced the winner of the 2017 presidential election. He officially became the President of Somaliland on 13 December 2017. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Somaliland Category:Current national leaders
